channel.title: I am looking for a rs privet server
channel.description:
Hello, lets just start with saying.. I AM A COMPLETE N00B. :palm:
I have been writing in Java for a while in some high school comp sic courses. I have been playing RS for years and I recently was brought upon this website and I am very excited! I am looking for Source code for a rs privet server that is almost the same as the original rs 07. I am am planing to play with it on my own, not for a profit benefit. I just want to learn a bit about it.
I was wondering if someone could link me to this source code?
oh! p.s I was hoping I could do this using something like Java Eclipse
Just to clarify i'm just looking for the client source code
